[Main]
Name=peek_w
Type=Function
Subtype=Macro
Header Files=peekpoke.h
Definition=#define peek_w(addr) (*((unsigned short*)(long)(addr)))

[Description]
Fetches a word from the memory.

[Explanation]
peek_w is like <A HREF="$$LINK(peek)">peek</A>, but fetches a word from the memory instead of
a byte.
<BR><BR>
<B>Note:</B> Do not use peek_w for reading I/O ports! Use <A HREF="$$LINK(peekIO_w)">peekIO_w</A> instead.
